<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Márcio — Desenvolvedor Full Stack & Arquiteto Cloud</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Portfólio de Márcio — Desenvolvedor Full Stack especializado em React, Node.js, Cloud Computing e Arquitetura de Software.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Josefin+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Open+Sans:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    :root {
      --primary: #1976D2;
      --primary-light: #42A5F5;
      --primary-dark: #1565C0;
      --primary-glow: rgba(25,118,210,0.3);
      --bg-dark: #0a0a0f;
      --bg-surface: #111118;
      --bg-card: #1a1a24;
      --bg-card-hover: #1e1e2e;
      --text-primary: #ffffff;
      --text-secondary: #a0a0b0;
      --text-muted: #6e6e7e;
      --border-subtle: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      --border-hover: rgba(66,165,245,0.2);
      --font-heading: 'Josefin Sans', sans-serif;
      --font-body: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
      --radius: 12px;
      --radius-sm: 8px;
      --radius-lg: 16px;
      --transition: 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
      --shadow-card: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      --shadow-hover: 0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    }

    body {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      background: var(--bg-surface);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      line-height: 1.7;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    a { color: var(--primary-light); text-decoration: none; transition: var(--transition); }
    a:hover { color: #fff; }

    img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; }

    .container { max-width: 1140px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }

    /* ===== PRELOADER ===== */
    .preloader {
      position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 9999;
      background: var(--bg-dark);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      flex-direction: column; gap: 24px;
      transition: opacity 0.6s ease, visibility 0.6s ease;
    }
    .preloader.hidden { opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; }
    .pl {
      position: relative; width: 60px; height: 60px;
      transform: perspective(120px) rotateX(30deg) rotateZ(45deg);
    }
    .pl__dot {
      position: absolute; width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 2px;
      background: var(--primary-light); top: 50%; left: 50%;
      animation: pushInOut 1.2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    .pl__dot:nth-child(1)  { transform: translate(-50%,-50%) rotate(0deg)   translate(24px) rotate(0deg);   animation-delay: 0s; }
    .pl__dot:nth-child(2)  { transform: translate(-50%,-50%) rotate(30deg)  translate(24px) rotate(-30deg);  animation-delay: .1s; }
    .pl__dot:nth-child(3)  { transform: translate(-50%,-50%) rotate(60deg)  translate(24px) rotate(-60deg);  animation-delay: .2s; }
    .pl__dot:nth-child(4)  { transform: translate(-50%,-50%) rotate(90deg)  translate(24px) rotate(-90deg);  animation-delay: .3s; }
    .pl__dot:nth-child(5)  { transform: translate(-50%,-50%) rotate(120deg) translate(24px) rotate(-120deg); animation-delay: .4s; }
    .pl__dot:nth-child(6)  { transform: translate(-50%,-50%) rotate(150deg) translate(24px) rotate(-150deg); animation-delay: .5s; }
    .pl__dot:nth-child(7)  { transform: translate(-50%,-50%) rotate(180deg) translate(24px) rotate(-180deg); animation-delay: .6s; }
    .pl__dot:nth-child(8)  { transform: translate(-50%,-50%) rotate(210deg) translate(24px) rotate(-210deg); animation-delay: .7s; }
    .pl__dot:nth-child(9)  { transform: translate(-50%,-50%) rotate(240deg) translate(24px) rotate(-240deg); animation-delay: .8s; }
    .pl__dot:nth-child(10) { transform: translate(-50%,-50%) rotate(270deg) translate(24px) rotate(-270deg); animation-delay: .9s; }
    .pl__dot:nth-child(11) { transform: translate(-50%,-50%) rotate(300deg) translate(24px) rotate(-300deg); animation-delay: 1s; }
    .pl__dot:nth-child(12) { transform: translate(-50%,-50%) rotate(330deg) translate(24px) rotate(-330deg); animation-delay: 1.1s; }
    @keyframes pushInOut {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: translate(-50%,-50%) scale(1); }
      50% { opacity: .5; transform: translate(-50%,-50%) scale(.3); }
    }
    .pl__text {
      font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted);
      letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* ===== NAVBAR ===== */
    .navbar {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 1000;
      background: rgba(10,10,15,0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(24px) saturate(1.2);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(24px) saturate(1.2);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      height: 68px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      transition: var(--transition);
    }
    .navbar .container {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; width: 100%;
    }
    .navbar-brand {
      font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 3px; color: #fff !important;
    }
    .navbar-brand span { color: var(--primary-light); }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a {
      font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); position: relative;
      padding: 22px 0; transition: var(--transition);
    }
    .nav-links a::after {
      content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 0; height: 2px; background: var(--primary-light);
      transition: var(--transition); border-radius: 2px;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover, .nav-links a.active { color: #fff; }
    .nav-links a:hover::after, .nav-links a.active::after { width: 100%; }
    .nav-links a.active::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -4px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--primary-light);
      animation: navDotPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes navDotPulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1); }
      50% { opacity: .3; transform: translateX(-50%) scale(.6); }
    }

    .nav-toggle {
      display: none; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; color: #fff; padding: 8px;
    }
    .nav-toggle svg { width: 36px; height: 36px; overflow: visible; }
    .nav-toggle .line { fill: none; stroke: currentColor; stroke-width: 4; stroke-linecap: round; transition: stroke-dasharray .4s, stroke-dashoffset .4s; }
    .nav-toggle .top { stroke-dasharray: 40 139; }
    .nav-toggle .bottom { stroke-dasharray: 40 180; }
    .nav-toggle.active .top { stroke-dashoffset: -98px; }
    .nav-toggle.active .bottom { stroke-dashoffset: -138px; }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-toggle { display: block; }
      .nav-links {
        display: none; position: absolute; top: 68px; left: 0; right: 0;
        background: rgba(10,10,15,0.97); backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
        flex-direction: column; padding: 8px 24px; gap: 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      }
      .nav-links.open { display: flex; }
      .nav-links a { padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle); }
    }

    /* ===== HERO ===== */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--bg-dark);
      padding-top: 68px;
    }
    .hero-bg {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 50%, rgba(25,118,210,0.12) 0%, transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 50%, rgba(66,165,245,0.08) 0%, transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 100%, rgba(10,10,15,1) 0%, transparent 40%);
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .hero .container {
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; align-items: center;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero .container { grid-template-columns: 1fr; text-align: center; gap: 40px; }
      .hero-image { order: -1; }
    }
    .hero-greeting {
      font-size: 13px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 3px;
      color: var(--primary-light); margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 600;
    }
    .hero-name {
      font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: clamp(38px, 5vw, 56px);
      font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .hero-title {
      font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 20px);
      font-weight: 300; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 20px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .hero-desc {
      color: var(--text-secondary); max-width: 520px; margin-bottom: 28px;
      font-weight: 300; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .hero-desc { margin: 0 auto 28px; } }
    .hero-cta { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .hero-cta { justify-content: center; } }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 30px; font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px;
      transition: var(--transition); cursor: pointer; border: none; font-weight: 500;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--primary); color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px var(--primary-glow);
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .btn-primary::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.1), transparent);
      transform: translateX(-100%);
      transition: transform 0.6s;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: var(--primary-dark); transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.02);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 40px var(--primary-glow); color: #fff;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover::before { transform: translateX(100%); }
    .btn-outline {
      background: transparent; color: var(--primary-light);
      border: 2px solid var(--primary-light); position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .btn-outline::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: var(--primary);
      transform: scaleX(0); transform-origin: right;
      transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1); z-index: -1;
    }
    .btn-outline:hover {
      color: #fff; border-color: var(--primary); transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px var(--primary-glow);
    }
    .btn-outline:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); transform-origin: left; }
    .btn-glass {
      background: rgba(25,118,210,0.12); color: #fff;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border: 1px solid rgba(66,165,245,0.2);
    }
    .btn-glass:hover { background: rgba(25,118,210,0.3); transform: translateY(-3px); color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 8px 30px var(--primary-glow); }

    .hero-image {
      display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;
    }
    .hero-image-wrap {
      width: 320px; height: 320px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-light));
      padding: 4px; position: relative;
      box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(25,118,210,0.2);
      animation: heroGlow 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes heroGlow {
      0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(25,118,210,0.2); }
      50% { box-shadow: 0 0 80px rgba(25,118,210,0.35); }
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .hero-image-wrap { width: 220px; height: 220px; } }
    .hero-image-inner {
      width: 100%; height: 100%; border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--bg-dark);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 100px; color: rgba(66,165,245,0.15); overflow: hidden;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .hero-image-inner { font-size: 70px; } }
    .hero-image-inner img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 50%; }

    .scroll-indicator {
      position: absolute; bottom: 32px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
      z-index: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
      gap: 8px; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px; transition: var(--transition); cursor: pointer;
    }
    .scroll-indicator:hover { color: var(--primary-light); }
    .scroll-mouse {
      width: 24px; height: 36px; border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      border-radius: 12px; position: relative;
    }
    .scroll-wheel {
      width: 3px; height: 8px; border-radius: 2px;
      background: var(--primary-light);
      position: absolute; top: 6px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
      animation: scrollWheel 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes scrollWheel {
      0% { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
      100% { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(14px); }
    }

    /* ===== SECTION COMMON ===== */
    .section {
      padding: 100px 0; position: relative;
    }
    .section-dark { background: var(--bg-dark); }

    .section-head {
      text-align: center; margin-bottom: 56px;
    }
    .section-head span {
      font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 3px;
      color: var(--primary-light); font-weight: 600; display: block; margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .section-head h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 3px; color: #fff;
    }

    /* ===== ABOUT ===== */
    .about-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr; gap: 60px; align-items: center;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; } }

    .about-text h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 26px; font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .about-text > p {
      color: var(--text-secondary); font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 15px;
    }
    .about-text strong { color: #fff; }

    .about-image img {
      width: 100%; border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
    }
    .about-image .placeholder-img {
      width: 100%; border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--bg-card), #111122);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      aspect-ratio: 4/3;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 80px; color: rgba(66,165,245,0.12);
    }

    .about-highlights {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 16px; margin-top: 48px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .about-highlights { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
    .highlight-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 24px 16px; text-align: center;
      transition: var(--transition);
    }
    .highlight-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px); border-color: var(--border-hover);
      background: rgba(25,118,210,0.06);
    }
    .highlight-number {
      font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--primary-light); line-height: 1;
    }
    .highlight-label {
      font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 8px;
    }

    /* ===== SKILLS ===== */
    .skills-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 992px) { .skills-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
    @media (max-width: 480px) { .skills-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

    .skill-card {
      background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 32px 24px;
      transition: var(--transition); position: relative; overflow: hidden;
      cursor: default;
    }
    .skill-card::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--primary), transparent);
      transform: scaleX(0); transition: var(--transition);
    }
    .skill-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px); border-color: var(--border-hover);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover); background: var(--bg-card-hover);
    }
    .skill-card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }

    .skill-icon {
      width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      background: rgba(25,118,210,0.12);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 22px; color: var(--primary-light); margin-bottom: 16px;
      transition: var(--transition);
    }
    .skill-card:hover .skill-icon { background: rgba(25,118,210,0.2); transform: scale(1.05); }

    .skill-card h5 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .skill-card p {
      font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ===== CERTIFICATIONS ===== */
    .certs-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 20px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 992px) { .certs-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); } }
    @media (max-width: 600px) { .certs-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }

    .cert-card {
      background: var(--bg-surface); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 28px 20px; text-align: center;
      transition: var(--transition);
    }
    .cert-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px); border-color: var(--border-hover);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }
    .cert-icon {
      width: 56px; height: 56px; margin: 0 auto 16px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 26px; color: var(--primary-light);
    }
    .cert-card h6 { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .cert-card p { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .cert-card a {
      font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ===== RESUME SECTION ===== */
    .resume-cta {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(25,118,210,0.08), rgba(25,118,210,0.02));
      border: 1px solid var(--border-hover);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 56px 40px;
      text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .resume-cta h3 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 26px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .resume-cta p { color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 28px; font-size: 15px; }
    .resume-cta .btn { padding: 16px 40px; }

    /* ===== TIMELINE ===== */
    .timeline {
      position: relative; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .timeline::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; left: 24px; top: 0; bottom: 0;
      width: 1px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .timeline::before { left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); }
    }
    .timeline-item {
      position: relative; padding-left: 60px; padding-bottom: 48px;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .timeline-item {
        width: 50%; padding-left: 0;
      }
      .timeline-item:nth-child(odd) { padding-right: 40px; text-align: right; }
      .timeline-item:nth-child(even) { margin-left: 50%; padding-left: 40px; text-align: left; }
    }
    .timeline-dot {
      position: absolute; left: 16px; top: 4px;
      width: 16px; height: 16px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--bg-dark); border: 3px solid var(--primary-light);
      z-index: 1;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .timeline-dot { left: auto; right: -8px; }
      .timeline-item:nth-child(even) .timeline-dot { left: -8px; right: auto; }
    }
    .timeline-date {
      font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px;
      color: var(--primary-light); margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600;
    }
    .timeline-company {
      font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .timeline-role {
      font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .timeline-desc {
      font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .timeline-desc ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
    .timeline-desc li { margin-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 20px; position: relative; }
    .timeline-desc li::before {
      content: '▹'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--primary-light);
    }

    /* ===== PROJECTS ===== */
    .projects-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 24px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .projects-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

    .project-card {
      background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden;
      transition: var(--transition); position: relative;
    }
    .project-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px); border-color: var(--border-hover);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover);
    }
    .project-thumb {
      height: 200px; background: #12121e;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 48px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .project-thumb img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
    .project-body { padding: 24px; }
    .project-body h5 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .project-body p {
      font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .project-tags {
      display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .project-tags span {
      padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 10px;
      background: rgba(25,118,210,0.1); color: var(--primary-light);
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; font-weight: 600;
    }
    .project-links { display: flex; gap: 16px; }
    .project-links a {
      font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ===== ACHIEVEMENTS ===== */
    .achievements-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .achievements-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
    @media (max-width: 480px) { .achievements-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

    .achievement-card {
      background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 28px 24px; text-align: center;
      transition: var(--transition);
    }
    .achievement-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px); border-color: var(--border-hover);
      background: var(--bg-card-hover);
    }
    .achievement-icon {
      font-size: 32px; color: var(--primary-light); margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .achievement-card h5 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .achievement-card p {
      font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-secondary);
    }

    /* ===== COMMUNITY ===== */
    .community-stats {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .community-stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
    .community-stat {
      text-align: center; padding: 24px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      border-radius: var(--radius); transition: var(--transition);
    }
    .community-stat:hover {
      border-color: var(--border-hover); transform: translateY(-4px);
    }
    .community-stat .stat-num {
      font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 38px; font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--primary-light); line-height: 1;
    }
    .community-stat p {
      font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .community-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 20px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) { .community-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    .community-card {
      background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 24px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; transition: var(--transition);
    }
    .community-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px); border-color: var(--border-hover);
    }
    .community-card-icon {
      width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      background: rgba(25,118,210,0.1); flex-shrink: 0;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 20px; color: var(--primary-light);
    }
    .community-card-content h6 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 2px;
    }
    .community-card-content span {
      font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-secondary);
    }

    /* ===== CONTACT ===== */
    .contact-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 48px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; } }

    .contact-info h3 {
      font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .contact-info > p {
      color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 28px; font-size: 15px;
    }

    .contact-item {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .contact-item-icon {
      width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(25,118,210,0.1); flex-shrink: 0;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 18px; color: var(--primary-light);
    }
    .contact-item-text h6 {
      font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 2px;
    }
    .contact-item-text span { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-secondary); }

    .contact-social {
      display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-top: 32px;
    }
    .contact-social a {
      width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary);
      transition: var(--transition);
    }
    .contact-social a:hover {
      background: var(--primary); color: #fff; border-color: var(--primary);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--primary-glow);
    }

    .contact-form input,
    .contact-form textarea {
      width: 100%; padding: 14px 18px; margin-bottom: 16px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm); color: #fff; font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 14px; transition: var(--transition);
    }
    .contact-form input:focus,
    .contact-form textarea:focus {
      outline: none; border-color: var(--primary);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(25,118,210,0.1);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }
    .contact-form textarea { height: 140px; resize: vertical; }
    .contact-form .btn { width: 100%; justify-content: center; padding: 16px; }

    /* ===== FOOTER ===== */
    .footer {
      background: rgba(10,10,15,0.8); backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
      padding: 32px 0; text-align: center;
    }
    .footer-links { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .footer-links a {
      font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); transition: var(--transition);
    }
    .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--primary-light); text-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--primary-glow); }
    .footer p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); }
    .footer p a { color: var(--primary-light); }

    .back-to-top {
      position: fixed; bottom: 24px; right: 24px; z-index: 99;
      width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--primary); color: #fff; border: none;
      cursor: pointer; font-size: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px var(--primary-glow);
      transition: var(--transition); opacity: 0; visibility: hidden;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    .back-to-top.visible { opacity: 1; visibility: visible; transform: translateY(0); }
    .back-to-top:hover { background: var(--primary-dark); transform: translateY(-3px); }

    /* ===== ANIMATIONS ===== */
    .fade-up {
      opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px);
      filter: blur(4px);
      transition: opacity 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1),
                  transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1),
                  filter 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    }
    .fade-up.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); filter: blur(0); }

    /* Scale-in variant for cards */
    .scale-in {
      opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.9);
      transition: opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1),
                  transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    }
    .scale-in.visible { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }

    /* Stagger delays for grid children */
    .skills-grid .fade-up:nth-child(1),
    .certs-grid .fade-up:nth-child(1),
    .projects-grid .fade-up:nth-child(1),
    .achievements-grid .fade-up:nth-child(1),
    .community-stats .fade-up:nth-child(1),
    .community-grid .fade-up:nth-child(1) { transition-delay: 0s; }

    .skills-grid .fade-up:nth-child(2),
    .certs-grid .fade-up:nth-child(2),
    .projects-grid .fade-up:nth-child(2),
    .achievements-grid .fade-up:nth-child(2),
    .community-stats .fade-up:nth-child(2),
    .community-grid .fade-up:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: 0.05s; }

    .skills-grid .fade-up:nth-child(3),
    .certs-grid .fade-up:nth-child(3),
    .projects-grid .fade-up:nth-child(3),
    .achievements-grid .fade-up:nth-child(3),
    .community-stats .fade-up:nth-child(3),
    .community-grid .fade-up:nth-child(3) { transition-delay: 0.1s; }

    .skills-grid .fade-up:nth-child(4),
    .certs-grid .fade-up:nth-child(4),
    .projects-grid .fade-up:nth-child(4),
    .achievements-grid .fade-up:nth-child(4),
    .community-stats .fade-up:nth-child(4),
    .community-grid .fade-up:nth-child(4) { transition-delay: 0.15s; }

    .skills-grid .fade-up:nth-child(5),
    .certs-grid .fade-up:nth-child(5),
    .community-stats .fade-up:nth-child(5) { transition-delay: 0.2s; }

    .skills-grid .fade-up:nth-child(6),
    .certs-grid .fade-up:nth-child(6),
    .community-stats .fade-up:nth-child(6) { transition-delay: 0.25s; }

    .certs-grid .fade-up:nth-child(7) { transition-delay: 0.3s; }
    .certs-grid .fade-up:nth-child(8) { transition-delay: 0.35s; }

    /* Timeline staggered */
    .timeline-item:nth-child(1) .fade-up { transition-delay: 0s; }
    .timeline-item:nth-child(2) .fade-up { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
    .timeline-item:nth-child(3) .fade-up { transition-delay: 0.2s; }

    /* ===== PARTICLE BACKGROUND ===== */
    #particle-canvas {
      position: fixed; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
    }
    .section > .container { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .hero .container { z-index: 1; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- PRELOADER -->
  <div class="preloader" id="preloader">
    <div class="pl">
      <div class="pl__dot"></div><div class="pl__dot"></div><div class="pl__dot"></div>
      <div class="pl__dot"></div><div class="pl__dot"></div><div class="pl__dot"></div>
      <div class="pl__dot"></div><div class="pl__dot"></div><div class="pl__dot"></div>
      <div class="pl__dot"></div><div class="pl__dot"></div><div class="pl__dot"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="pl__text">Carregando…</div>
  </div>

  <!-- NAVBAR -->
  <nav class="navbar" id="navbar">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="#" class="navbar-brand">Már<span>cio</span></a>
      <button class="nav-toggle" id="navToggle" aria-label="Menu">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100">
          <path class="line top" d="m 30,33 h 40 c 0,0 9.044436,-0.654587 9.044436,-8.508902 0,-7.854315 -8.024349,-11.958003 -14.89975,-10.85914 -6.875401,1.098863 -13.637059,4.171617 -13.637059,16.368042 v 40"/>
          <path class="line middle" d="m 30,50 h 40"/>
          <path class="line bottom" d="m 30,67 h 40 c 12.796276,0 15.357889,-11.717785 15.357889,-26.851538 0,-15.133752 -4.786586,-27.274118 -16.667516,-27.274118 -11.88093,0 -18.499247,6.994427 -18.435284,17.125656 l 0.252538,40"/>
        </svg>
      </button>
      <ul class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
        <li><a href="#home" class="active">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="#about">Sobre</a></li>
        <li><a href="#skills">Habilidades</a></li>
        <li><a href="#experience">Experiência</a></li>
        <li><a href="#projects">Projetos</a></li>
        <li><a href="#contact">Contato</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero" id="home">
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <p class="hero-greeting">Olá, eu sou</p>
        <h1 class="hero-name">Márcio</h1>
        <p class="hero-title">Desenvolvedor Full Stack & Arquiteto Cloud</p>
        <p class="hero-desc">
          Especializado em construir aplicações web escaláveis, arquiteturas em nuvem e sistemas distribuídos.
          Apaixonado por transformar ideias complexas em soluções digitais de alto impacto.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-cta">
          <a href="#projects" class="btn btn-primary">
            <i class="fas fa-eye"></i> Ver Projetos
          </a>
          <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline">
            <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Contato
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-glass">
            <i class="fas fa-download"></i> Currículo
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-image">
        <div class="hero-image-wrap">
          <div class="hero-image-inner">
            <i class="fas fa-user-astronaut"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a href="#about" class="scroll-indicator" aria-label="Rolar para baixo">
      <div class="scroll-mouse"><div class="scroll-wheel"></div></div>
      <span>Rolar</span>
    </a>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section class="section" id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head fade-up">
        <span>Sobre mim</span>
        <h2>Quem sou eu</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-text fade-up">
          <h2>Desenvolvedor Full Stack &<br>Arquiteto de Software</h2>
          <p>
            Sou um desenvolvedor com <strong>+5 anos de experiência</strong> construindo aplicações web modernas,
            escaláveis e de alto desempenho. Minha jornada começou com a curiosidade por entender como a tecnologia
            pode resolver problemas reais — e se transformou em uma carreira dedicada à excelência técnica.
          </p>
          <p>
            Hoje trabalho com <strong>React, Next.js, Node.js e TypeScript</strong> no front-end, e
            <strong>Python, Go e arquiteturas Cloud</strong> no back-end. Sou entusiasta de <strong>DevOps,
            Kubernetes, e sistemas distribuídos</strong>, sempre buscando as melhores práticas de engenharia
            de software.
          </p>
          <p>
            Acredito que tecnologia de qualidade começa com <strong>código limpo, testes sólidos e
            arquitetura bem pensada</strong>. Fora do código, sou mentor de desenvolvedores iniciantes,
            contribuidor open source e organizador de eventos técnicos.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-image fade-up">
          <div class="placeholder-img">
            <i class="fas fa-user-astronaut"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Highlights -->
      <div class="about-highlights">
        <div class="highlight-card fade-up">
          <div class="highlight-number"><span data-target="5">0</span>+</div>
          <p class="highlight-label">Anos de Experiência</p>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-card fade-up">
          <div class="highlight-number"><span data-target="30">0</span>+</div>
          <p class="highlight-label">Projetos Entregues</p>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-card fade-up">
          <div class="highlight-number"><span data-target="500">0</span>+</div>
          <p class="highlight-label">Commits no GitHub</p>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-card fade-up">
          <div class="highlight-number"><span data-target="10">0</span>+</div>
          <p class="highlight-label">Certificações</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SKILLS -->
  <section class="section section-dark" id="skills">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head fade-up">
        <span>Minhas competências</span>
        <h2>Habilidades</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="skills-grid">
        <div class="skill-card fade-up">
          <div class="skill-icon"><i class="fab fa-react"></i></div>
          <h5>Front-End</h5>
          <p>React, Next.js, TypeScript, TailwindCSS. Criação de interfaces modernas, responsivas e performáticas com foco em experiência do usuário.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-card fade-up">
          <div class="skill-icon"><i class="fas fa-server"></i></div>
          <h5>Back-End</h5>
          <p>Node.js, Python (FastAPI, Django), Go. APIs RESTful e GraphQL, bancos SQL e NoSQL, autenticação, autorização e caching.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-card fade-up">
          <div class="skill-icon"><i class="fas fa-cloud"></i></div>
          <h5>Cloud & DevOps</h5>
          <p>Docker, Kubernetes, CI/CD (GitHub Actions), AWS/GCP. Infraestrutura como código com Terraform e monitoramento com Prometheus/Grafana.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-card fade-up">
          <div class="skill-icon"><i class="fas fa-sitemap"></i></div>
          <h5>Arquitetura</h5>
          <p>Microsserviços, event-driven architecture, clean architecture, DDD e padrões de design para sistemas escaláveis e resilientes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-card fade-up">
          <div class="skill-icon"><i class="fas fa-database"></i></div>
          <h5>Bancos de Dados</h5>
          <p>PostgreSQL, MongoDB, Redis, Elasticsearch. Modelagem, otimização de queries, replicação e estratégias de indexing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-card fade-up">
          <div class="skill-icon"><i class="fas fa-brain"></i></div>
          <h5>IA & Dados</h5>
          <p>Machine Learning, LLMs, processamento de dados com Python. Integração de modelos de IA em aplicações web e pipelines de dados.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CERTIFICATIONS -->
  <section class="section" id="certifications">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head fade-up">
        <span>Conhecimento validado</span>
        <h2>Certificações</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="certs-grid">
        <div class="cert-card scale-in">
          <div class="cert-icon"><i class="fab fa-aws"></i></div>
          <h6>AWS Certified</h6>
          <p>Solutions Architect</p>
          <a href="#">Verificar →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="cert-card scale-in">
          <div class="cert-icon"><i class="fab fa-google"></i></div>
          <h6>Google Cloud</h6>
          <p>Associate Cloud Engineer</p>
          <a href="#">Verificar →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="cert-card scale-in">
          <div class="cert-icon"><i class="fab fa-microsoft"></i></div>
          <h6>Azure AZ-900</h6>
          <p>Azure Fundamentals</p>
          <a href="#">Verificar →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="cert-card scale-in">
          <div class="cert-icon"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i></div>
          <h6>CompTIA Security+</h6>
          <p>Security Certification</p>
          <a href="#">Verificar →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="cert-card scale-in">
          <div class="cert-icon"><i class="fab fa-docker"></i></div>
          <h6>Docker</h6>
          <p>Docker Certified Associate</p>
          <a href="#">Verificar →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="cert-card scale-in">
          <div class="cert-icon"><i class="fab fa-linux"></i></div>
          <h6>Linux Professional</h6>
          <p>LPIC-1 Certified</p>
          <a href="#">Verificar →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="cert-card scale-in">
          <div class="cert-icon"><i class="fas fa-database"></i></div>
          <h6>MongoDB</h6>
          <p>Associate Developer</p>
          <a href="#">Verificar →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="cert-card scale-in">
          <div class="cert-icon"><i class="fas fa-project-diagram"></i></div>
          <h6>Scrum Master</h6>
          <p>Professional Scrum Master</p>
          <a href="#">Verificar →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- RESUME CTA -->
  <section class="section section-dark" id="resume">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="resume-cta fade-up">
        <i class="fas fa-file-alt" style="font-size: 40px; color: var(--primary-light); margin-bottom: 16px;"></i>
        <h3>Currículo Completo</h3>
        <p>Baixe meu currículo para uma visão detalhada da minha trajetória profissional, educação, certificações e projetos.</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">
          <i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download CV
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- EXPERIENCE / TIMELINE -->
  <section class="section" id="experience">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head fade-up">
        <span>Trajetória profissional</span>
        <h2>Experiência</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item fade-up">
          <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
          <div class="timeline-date">2024 — Presente</div>
          <div class="timeline-company">TechCorp Solutions</div>
          <div class="timeline-role">Desenvolvedor Full Stack Sênior</div>
          <div class="timeline-desc">
            <ul>
              <li>Liderou a migração de arquitetura monolítica para microsserviços, reduzindo o tempo de deploy em 70%</li>
              <li>Projetou sistema de cache distribuído com Redis, melhorando a latência das APIs em 60%</li>
              <li>Implementou pipeline CI/CD com GitHub Actions e Docker, automatizando testes e deploys</li>
              <li>Mentoria técnica de 4 desenvolvedores juniores no squad</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item fade-up">
          <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
          <div class="timeline-date">2022 — 2024</div>
          <div class="timeline-company">StartupInova</div>
          <div class="timeline-role">Desenvolvedor Full Stack Pleno</div>
          <div class="timeline-desc">
            <ul>
              <li>Desenvolveu plataforma SaaS de analytics processando 2M+ eventos/dia com Python e PostgreSQL</li>
              <li>Criou dashboard interativo em React com visualizações em tempo real usando WebSockets</li>
              <li>Reduziu custos de infraestrutura em 40% otimizando queries e implementando caching</li>
              <li>Contribuiu para a arquitetura do sistema, resultando em aumento de 95% na cobertura de testes</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item fade-up">
          <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
